<TEXT>
<P>
After watching the newly extended "Home" program, I've decided to express my 
opinion. I am disappointed as to how it has changed. Those things that made the 
show a success just aren't there anymore, such as the information on improving 
one's home or creative ideas for one's hobbies. Seems as if "Home" has become 
just another talk show. Also, Sandy Hill was a wonderful hostess and I think 
Cristina Ferrare should have stayed on "AM." 
</P>
<P>
Elizabeth Sanchez, Norwalk 
</P>
</TEXT>
