<TEXT>
<P>
Thanks, NBC, for the exciting miniseries, "Brotherhood of the Rose." I had 
thoroughly enjoyed reading the novel and looked forward to the TV adaptation. I 
was not disappointed. Great acting and a well-chosen cast combined to make the 
characters in the book come to life. 
</P>
<P>
Elaine Schaeffer, Agoura 
</P>
</TEXT>
