<HEADLINE>
<P>
ANIMALS AS ACTORS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
As I have read about the "Project X" controversy, I have become more and more 
curious about how animals that work in movies are treated. 
</P>
<P>
According to the Los Angeles Times Magazine, Vicki Hearne's story was "The 
Trainers' Side of the Controversy." 
</P>
<P>
Now, I would like to hear the other side. 
</P>
<P>
WANDA BOWSER 
</P>
<P>
Mission Hills 
</P>
</TEXT>
