<P>
NANCY VALE'S NAME may be unfamiliar to Americans, but her sweaters are sold all 
over the country under Ralph Lauren, Calvin Klein and other labels. The 
sweaters are gorgeous, from a thick Navajo-style cardigan to an Early American 
