Oscar Reiss Children's Workers, an auxiliary of the Reiss-Davis Child Study 
Center, goes gala Wednesday evening at the Wiltern Theatre with a Johnny Mathis 
evening preceded by a cocktail buffet at the Los Angeles Club. Sylvia Trust and 
Dorie Gold are co-chairs. . . . 
</P>
