ORGANIZED CRIME; WHITE COLLAR CRIME; SECURITIES FRAUD; FUTURES TRADING; 
COMMODITIES; COMMODITY EXCHANGES; CHICAGO MERCANTILE EXCHANGE; CHICAGO BOARD OF 
TRADE; POLITICAL CORRUPTION 
</P>
