<HEADLINE>
<P>
BAKER, SHEVARDNADZE TO MEET NEXT MONTH 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
From Reuters 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
WASHINGTON 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Secretary of State James A. Baker III is to meet Soviet Foreign Minister Eduard 
A Shevardnadze in Vienna on March 7 for a get-acquainted session, the State 
Department said. Friday. 
</P>
<P>
