<HEADLINE>
<P>
BRIEFCASE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Richard C. Celio has joined Carl Karcher Enterprises in the new position of 
vice president and corporate counsel. Previously, he was a partner in the law 
firm of Holden, Fergus &amp; Celio. Carl Karcher Enterprises is the parent for 
more than 480 Carl's Jr. restaurants in California, Arizona, Nevada and Oregon. 
</P>
